&quot;Some British and Canadian CD releases include four to six additional tracks [THIS ONE]. The first four are from the John Peel Radio sessions. The other tracks were recorded for an unreleased single which was to have been the band&amp;#039;s first release. Gordon Sharp of Cindytalk provided backup vocals on Dear Heart and Hazel.&quot;


&quot;Dear Heart&quot;
&quot;Hazel&quot;
&quot;Hearsay Please&quot;
&quot;Blind Dumb Deaf&quot;
&quot;Speak No Evil&quot;
